@startuml

title Door1 - State Diagram

hide empty description
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam noteBorderColor #888888

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<idle>> #E8F4F8
    BackgroundColor<<moving>> #FFE8CC
    BorderColor #444444
}

[*] --> Closed

state Closed   <<idle>>
state Open     <<idle>>
state StayOpen <<idle>>
state Opening  <<moving>>
state Closing  <<moving>>

Closed   --> Opening  : click
Opening  --> Closing  : click
Opening  --> Open     : complete
Closing  --> Opening  : click
Closing  --> Closed   : complete
Open     --> StayOpen : click
Open     --> Closing  : timeout
StayOpen --> Closing  : click, timeout

note right of Closed
  <b>초기 상태</b>
  문이 완전히 닫혀 있음
end note

note right of Opening
  <b>전이 상태 (모터 동작 중)</b>
  complete 신호로 Open으로 이동
  click 시 즉시 Closing으로 반전
end note

note left of Open
  <b>대기 상태</b>
  click → 사용자가 계속 열어둠
  timeout → 자동 닫힘
end note

note left of StayOpen
  <b>강제 개방 상태</b>
  click 또는 timeout으로 닫힘
end note

note bottom
  <b>범례</b>
  ◼ 파란색 = 정지 상태 (idle)
  ◼ 주황색 = 동작 상태 (moving, 모터 가동)
  ──
  <b>이벤트</b>
  click    : 버튼 입력
  complete : 모터 동작 완료
  timeout  : 일정 시간 경과
end note

@enduml

/'@startuml

title Door1 - State Diagram 
[*] --> Closed

Closed --> Opening : click
Opening --> Closing : click
Closing --> Opening : click
Opening --> Open : complete
Open --> StayOpen : click
StayOpen --> Closing : click, timeout
Open --> Closing : timeout
Closing --> Closed : complete

@enduml'/